Apple Watch Q4 2015 Sales Estimates: How Many Smartwatches Did Apple Inc. Sell? 
IBTimes Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
It's been over six months since the launch of the Apple Watch and to put it mildly, Apple hasn't been too open with its sales figures. "We are not announcing the numbers," Apple CEO Tim Cook...
